title: CFP Rankings Release Tonight
description:
Joey Galloway, Wendi Mix, Rod Gilmore, and Heather Dinich will give their predictions on the CFP Rankings release and discuss who's in and who's out in the College Football Playoff Race. Joe Montana also joins the show and talks about the College Football Landscape as the season comes down to an end.
